<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28May1930"><font color="red">28 May 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Helen Fleischmann): He would like you please to send him a book called &ldquo;Sampson the Nazarite&rdquo; just published by Martin Secker &hellip; he is very much bored with the stupid newspapers which seem to be the only thing we can find to read to him so is anxious to have this book the subject of which interests him </div>
